            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "金價升穿4800美元 霍爾木茲海峽重開拖累油價急跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金價持續上升，現貨金報每盎司4828.3美元，升幅0.8%，本周累計上升1.7%。紐約期金收市報每盎司4879.6美元，升幅約1.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">霍爾木茲海峽重新開放後，油價急跌，市場預期此舉有助紓緩通脹壓力，並重燃市場對減息的預期。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15887934-%e9%87%91%e5%83%b9%e5%8d%87%e7%a9%bf4800%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83-%e9%9c%8d%e7%88%be%e6%9c%a8%e8%8c%b2%e6%b5%b7%e5%b3%bd%e9%87%8d%e9%96%8b%e6%8b%96%e7%b4%af%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e6%80%a5%e8%b7%8c",
